<p>EcoVentures: Focus on the Gulf is a multimedia CD designed to help middle school students learn about the Gulf of Mexicoâ€™s aquatic environment and the issues associated with protecting and managing aquatic resources. Students enter the world of a fictional National Park to explore a variety of ecosystems and develop a management plan for the park. There are on-line activities, expert consultants, and a video encyclopedia.</p>

